resources.string: This symptom analyzer is intended for informational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of something you have read on this symptom checker. The tool does not provide a definitive medical diagnosis and should be used as a guide to help you understand possible conditions based on your symptoms.
